OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FBlind and partially sighted people in
OL,7,FWales are being hit harder by the cost
OL,8,Fof living crisis compared to the
OL,9,Fgeneral population.
OL,11,FThat's according to a report by the
OL,12,FRoyal National Institute of Blind
OL,13,FPeople (RNIB) which has found that 1
OL,14,Fin 5 blind or partially sighted people
OL,15,Fhave to spend over #200 extra every
OL,16,Fmonth on unavoidable extra costs
OL,17,Fassociated with their disability.
