OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FAnum has macular degeneration, meaning
OL,7,Fshe is losing her sight over time. She
OL,8,Fwas a pharmacist for twelve years
OL,9,Funtil her eyesight deteriorated so
OL,10,Fmuch that she had to give up her
OL,11,Fcareer in 2019.
OL,13,FShe said the rising cost of taxi fares
OL,14,Fand difficulty using public transport
OL,15,Fhas left her feeling "isolated".
OL,17,F"Transportation is a big issue for
OL,18,Fme." She said.
