OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"I find it quite difficult to use on
OL,7,Fmy own independently, I'm relying on
OL,8,Ftaxis and nowadays taxi fares are
OL,9,Fgetting more and more expensive, which
OL,10,Fmeans I can't really go out and about.
OL,12,F"Because of the cost and thinking
OL,13,Fabout money, I tend to not use taxis
OL,14,Fas much anymore so I feel like I'm at
OL,15,Fhome more, I'm isolated more, I'm in
OL,16,Fthe house I'm not meeting my friends a
OL,17,Flot more.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
