OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"With the cost of living situation
OL,7,Fwe're in now with everything becoming
OL,8,Fmore expensive, budgeting is becoming
OL,9,Fmore important, I can't just decide I
OL,10,Fwant to go out whenever, it's not
OL,11,Fsomething I can do anymore.
OL,13,F"I feel isolated, I feel alone."
OL,15,FAnum explained that as a result of
OL,16,Fthese rising costs, she spends more
OL,17,Ftime at home,
