OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"I'm definitely feeling more
OL,7,Fhousebound in the sense that I can't
OL,8,Freally go places, I can't go to
OL,9,Factivities or events that I want to."
OL,11,FAnum said she also is spending more
OL,12,Fmoney on her weekly shop because she
OL,13,F"can't read the labels or any signage
OL,14,For anything so I don't know if there's
OL,15,Fa deal on or if there's something
OL,16,Fcheaper."
