OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"I feel very anxious and nervous going
OL,7,Fto the shops. You can ask for
OL,8,Fassistance but that depends on the
OL,9,Fperson - whether or not they're
OL,10,Fwilling to help you and a lot of the
OL,11,Ftime I've found that when I go to the
OL,12,Fshops it takes me a while even looking
OL,13,Ffor things.
OL,15,F"I've found that even people who do
OL,16,Fhelp, they don't really tell you about
OL,17,Fany deals or offers or if something's
OL,18,Freduced whereas if you had sight you'd
OL,19,Fbe able to explore that yourself.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/16
