OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"I feel a lot of the time that my
OL,7,Findependence has been taken away from
OL,8,Fme and having to depend on people is
OL,9,Fnot the nicest of feelings."
OL,11,FSteve, of Llantrisant, has been
OL,12,Fregistered blind for around ten years.
OL,13,FHe said he also often has to pay more
OL,14,Fon taxis as he sometimes struggles
OL,15,Frelying on public transport.
OL,17,F"I'm always wary when I go anywhere on
OL,18,Fpublic transport." He said.
