OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"Sometimes buses don't turn up or
OL,7,Ftrains get cancelled and I know you
OL,8,Fcan wait for the next one, but I get
OL,9,Fworried and nervous if I'm out and
OL,10,Fabout longer than I planned.
OL,12,F"I like to plan my days so I know
OL,13,Fwhat's happening and if I need to get
OL,14,Fa taxi, that takes a chunk out of my
OL,15,Fmoney that means I can't do something
OL,16,Felse."
