OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FHe also has difficulty accessing deals
OL,7,Fin shops: "Before I lost my sight I
OL,8,Fwas one of those people who would
OL,9,Falways go to the reduced fridge and
OL,10,Fget whatever's on offer, but now I
OL,11,Fdon't know where they are or what the
OL,12,Fspecial offers are."
OL,14,FHe added: "There are times where you
OL,15,Fthink 'I won't go out of the house
OL,16,Ftoday, it's easier'. But you've got to
OL,17,Fforce yourself to get up and go out
OL,18,Feveryday."
