OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FRNIB's report also found that one in
OL,7,Ffour blind or partially sighted adults
OL,8,Fof working age are in employment in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FLiz Williams, Policy and Public
OL,12,FAffairs Manager at RNIB Cymru: "We're
OL,13,Fgenuinely very concerned to see that
OL,14,Fblind and partially sighted people are
OL,15,Ffacing significant barriers to
OL,16,Faccessing work.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
