CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F466A1711810205
OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"Some of the main reasons they're
OL,7,Ffacing barriers to employment is that
OL,8,Femployers just don't understand the
OL,9,Freasonable adjustments that need to be
OL,10,Fput in place.
OL,12,F"They don't always see that blind and
OL,13,Fpartially sighted people can reach
OL,14,Ftheir potential and they can do a job
OL,15,Fwell, they just might need some extra
OL,16,Ftechnology or reasonable adjustments."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/16
