OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F466A1711810205
OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,F"That's a huge chunk of someone's
OL,7,Fmonthly income."
OL,9,F"We know that blind and partially
OL,10,Fsighted people are making less
OL,11,Fjourneys and we know that being able
OL,12,Fto access their communities - whether
OL,13,Fthat's via a train, a bus or a taxi,
OL,14,Fit's a real lifeline for blind and
OL,15,Fpartially sighted people, they can
OL,16,Fstay connected with friends, family
OL,17,Fand access those services and these
OL,18,Fthings are so important for our sense
OL,19,Fof belonging."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/16
