OL,3,CHow the cost of living is impacting
OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FShe added that this is also having an
OL,7,Fimpact on people accessing healthcare:
OL,8,F"Shockingly, fifteen percent of the
OL,9,Fpeople we spoke to missed a healthcare
OL,10,Fappointment because they couldn't
OL,11,Fafford to get to the GP surgery, they
OL,12,Fcouldn't afford to get to the hospital
OL,13,Fand that's really serious."
OL,15,FRNIB Cymru are calling on the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment to "incentivise public
OL,17,Fservices to make these reasonable
OL,18,Fadjustments so that they make the work
OL,19,Fplace accessible and that there's a
OL,20,Fculture there where employers want to
OL,21,Flearn and want to make things better."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
