OL,4,Cblind and partially sighted people
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our Disability Rights Taskforce are
OL,8,Fworking with disabled people and
OL,9,Forganisations, including the RNIB, to
OL,10,Fmake recommendations to improve the
OL,11,Flives of disabled people in Wales.
OL,12,FImproving employment and income,
OL,13,Faccess to services and travel are
OL,14,Fpriorities for the group.
